Ecological notes . This species has no commercial importan- ce in Brazil (as Bairdiella ronchus in
Itagaki et al ., 2007
). It is incidentally caught as bycatch in bottom trawls, gillnets, and seines, as well as by cast nets in mangrove swamps.

